Pending the results
of your internal review,

04:03.470 --> 04:07.634
There is no reason you
can't resume your job quickly.

04:07.640 --> 04:10.701
Do you miss it?

04:10.710 --> 04:13.680
I do. I love my job.

04:14.520 --> 04:18.684
But I feel like this career
belongs to beth davis,

04:18.690 --> 04:21.660
And now everyone
knows me as michelle.

04:21.660 --> 04:23.219
It's all over the news.

04:23.230 --> 04:25.426
Hmm.

04:25.430 --> 04:29.151
I changed my identity
when I was 20,

04:29.160 --> 04:31.959
So my entire adult life
has been spent

04:31.970 --> 04:34.359
As beth davis.

04:34.370 --> 04:37.965
I don't know who
michelle is anymore.

04:37.970 --> 04:40.359
Janice: Francine johnson
was stalked for several months

04:40.380 --> 04:42.371
By her abusive boyfriend
john murray.

04:42.380 --> 04:44.701
He was charged
with stalking, battery,

04:44.710 --> 04:46.747
Was sentenced to a year,
served 8 months,

04:46.750 --> 04:51.142
I just got confirmation that john
murray checked into a minnesota rehab

04:51.150 --> 04:53.414
There's no way he murdered
francine johnson.

04:53.420 --> 04:55.980
Well, I'll let baer
know. Thank you.

04:58.790 --> 05:00.781
Hey.

05:00.800 --> 05:04.668
You know, a stalking here,
a threat there.

05:04.670 --> 05:07.423
I'm good. I was
just in the building,

05:07.440 --> 05:09.169
So I thought I'd
come and say hi.

05:09.170 --> 05:10.990
Any idea when you're
coming back to work.

05:11.010 --> 05:14.878
It's been suggested
that I take some time off.

05:14.880 --> 05:18.771
I don't know.
Could be a while.

05:18.780 --> 05:20.305
Why? You don't think
I should?

05:20.320 --> 05:21.469
Oh, it's--it's not that.

05:21.480 --> 05:23.073
It's just that
you thrive on work,

05:23.090 --> 05:25.184
But, yeah, you should
take as much time as you need

05:25.190 --> 05:28.251
If that's what you want.

05:28.260 --> 05:29.011
Yeah.

05:29.020 --> 05:30.909
Janice: Hey, stranger.

05:30.930 --> 05:32.921
Hi!

05:32.930 --> 05:35.228
Much better.
They're gonna release him

05:35.230 --> 05:36.459
At the end
of the week.

05:36.470 --> 05:37.722
Great. I'm gonna
stop by the hospital

05:37.730 --> 05:40.427
On my way home.
He'd like that.

05:40.440 --> 05:41.839
Heh.
Heh.

05:41.840 --> 05:43.262
I'm gonna go.

05:43.270 --> 05:44.669
Come back to us, beth.

05:44.670 --> 05:45.808
Thanks.
Keep in touch.

05:45.810 --> 05:48.199
Hey. Uh, we should
get together for drinks

05:48.210 --> 05:49.439
Or something.

05:49.450 --> 05:51.475
You do owe me.

05:51.480 --> 05:52.379
For what?

05:52.380 --> 05:53.905
I saved your life.

05:53.920 --> 05:57.777
Well, I think that might
be worth a whole dinner,

05:57.790 --> 05:59.747
Don't you think?

06:02.620 --> 06:04.725
When you first filed a
report against your husband

06:04.730 --> 06:06.926
Darren tyler
3 months ago--

06:06.930 --> 06:08.329
All more 4 now.

06:08.330 --> 06:10.253
He was harassing you
over your breakup,

06:10.270 --> 06:13.729
Showing up at your work,
gym, restaurants.

06:13.740 --> 06:15.333
He was hurt,
he wanted you back.

06:15.340 --> 06:17.536
He can't understand
why I broke up with him.

06:17.540 --> 06:20.009
He only slept with every woman
who looked in his direction.

06:20.010 --> 06:21.808
Well, the judge granted
you a tro.

06:21.810 --> 06:23.369
Has he violated it?

06:23.380 --> 06:24.745
Yes.

06:24.750 --> 06:28.516
This morning, I found
this on my doorstep--

06:28.520 --> 06:30.409
My favorite bottle
of champagne

06:30.420 --> 06:33.720
Along with a play list
of taylor swift love songs.

06:33.720 --> 06:35.609
Does the music have
symbolic meaning?

06:35.620 --> 06:38.988
Do I look like I listen
to taylor swift?

06:38.990 --> 06:40.651
Are you sure darren
left these?

06:40.660 --> 06:42.321
Flowers last week,
perfume the week before.

06:42.330 --> 06:45.129
Well, you came to us because
he was threatening you.

06:45.130 --> 06:47.167
And now he's politely
stalking me. Whatever.

06:47.170 --> 06:48.899
I just want him
to stop.

06:48.900 --> 06:50.664
If you didn't see him
leave these things,

06:50.670 --> 06:51.831
Uh, we don't have
any proof.

06:51.840 --> 06:53.604
Well, I never saw him,
but I know it was him.

06:53.610 --> 06:55.669
Cheap flowers,
rank-ass-smelling perfume.

06:55.680 --> 06:58.103
I was married to the man.
He had zero taste.

06:58.110 --> 06:59.578
How can I get him
to stop?

06:59.580 --> 07:01.070
Well, he's trying
a different approach,

07:01.080 --> 07:03.777
Which indicates
an escalation.

07:03.790 --> 07:05.713
If he gets violent--
if?

07:05.720 --> 07:06.812
More like when.

07:06.820 --> 07:07.890
Darren has a temper.

07:07.890 --> 07:09.187
These gifts
don't fool me.

07:09.190 --> 07:11.830
He's one love song
away from snapping.

07:11.830 --> 07:12.888
He's not right
in his head.

07:12.900 --> 07:15.722
Look. I have done
everything you told me to do.

07:15.730 --> 07:18.529
I got a restraining order,
I changed my schedule,

07:18.530 --> 07:20.020
I take a different route
home every day,

07:20.040 --> 07:21.599
I shop
at 10 different stores.

07:21.600 --> 07:23.830
The only thing left
for me to do is to move.

07:23.840 --> 07:26.639
I can't afford to move.
I have a job here.

07:26.640 --> 07:28.904
He is ruining
my life.

07:28.910 --> 07:32.039
Can you just arrest
his ass?

07:36.950 --> 07:38.611
I don't scare easily,

07:38.620 --> 07:40.941
But this is
really getting to me.

07:40.960 --> 07:43.554
Look. I'll talk
to him.

07:43.560 --> 07:47.986
We're gonna get you
through this, I promise.

07:52.800 --> 07:56.737
Hi. I'm looking
for vicky gregg.

08:03.110 --> 08:05.101
Will!

08:05.110 --> 08:05.770
Hey.

08:05.780 --> 08:07.145
What are you
doing here?

08:07.150 --> 08:08.743
Didn't you get
my message?

08:08.750 --> 08:10.172
Didn't you get mine?

08:10.190 --> 08:12.545
[sighs]

08:12.550 --> 08:14.609
Come in here.

08:23.130 --> 08:24.552
Who's the, uh--

08:24.570 --> 08:25.321
No idea.

08:25.330 --> 08:26.627
Why are you here, will?

08:26.640 --> 08:28.995
It's good to see
you, too, vicky.

08:29.000 --> 08:29.865
Please.

08:29.870 --> 08:32.339
No. Don't sit down.
You're not staying.

08:32.340 --> 08:34.229
I left you a message.
I can't have lunch.

08:34.240 --> 08:35.707
How about dinner?
No.

08:35.710 --> 08:37.075
Drinks later?
No.

08:37.080 --> 08:38.548
Why not?
Because.

08:38.549 --> 08:40.700
You say so much
with so little.

08:40.720 --> 08:43.371
I'm sorry, will. This
really not a good time.

08:43.390 --> 08:45.518
Well, that sums up
our entire marriage.

08:45.520 --> 08:47.488
Can you please leave
before I throw something?

08:47.490 --> 08:51.779
I've missed you. No one
berates me the way you do.

08:51.790 --> 08:53.326
How long are you
in town for?

08:53.330 --> 08:54.684
I don't know yet.

08:54.700 --> 08:56.623
I want to sell
the house.

08:56.630 --> 09:00.191
It's the last remaining
detail of your divorce.

09:00.200 --> 09:01.634
Our divorce.

09:01.640 --> 09:03.836
Heh. Yeah.

09:03.840 --> 09:07.299
When can we discuss it?

09:07.310 --> 09:08.630
Before I leave.

09:08.640 --> 09:11.234
I promise you
I'll call you.

09:12.850 --> 09:15.171
I'll hold you to it.

09:52.090 --> 09:54.957
[dog barking]

10:01.630 --> 10:03.928
